Calvin,
how you doing on your side?

00:17.756 --> 00:19.149
I'm good.

00:19.193 --> 00:21.021
Oh.

00:23.936 --> 00:25.764
Whoa! What's that?

00:25.808 --> 00:27.070
I have no idea.

00:27.114 --> 00:28.811
It just got delivered
from my Grandpa Ed.

00:28.854 --> 00:30.552
Well, it's not complainingabout my cooking,

00:30.595 --> 00:32.641
so it can't beGrandma Jean.

00:32.684 --> 00:36.253
All right, well, Calvin,help me open this thing up.All right.

00:39.430 --> 00:41.519
