00:47.134 --> 00:48.744
this is not your grandmother?

00:51.355 --> 00:53.314
I can't believe it.

00:53.357 --> 00:55.707
He gave me his
moose head.

00:55.751 --> 00:57.535
Why would your grandfather
send you that?

00:57.579 --> 01:00.843
It looked so good in Michigan
where I couldn't see it.

01:00.886 --> 01:03.454
He must've remembered how much
I love this thing. You know,

01:03.498 --> 01:04.716
I was actually with him

01:04.760 --> 01:07.937
when he brought this
magnificent beast down.

01:07.980 --> 01:09.591
I didn't knowyou used to hunt.

01:09.634 --> 01:11.636
Oh, I didn't. We were
driving to mini golf,

01:11.680 --> 01:14.117
and he hit it
on Route 43.

01:15.205 --> 01:17.642
I know how you feel, buddy.

01:17.686 --> 01:20.906
I never saw Dave coming, either.

01:20.950 --> 01:22.865
